    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我把Alice放在aqua色的box里，offer-up.contract放在skyblue的Contract box中。这里用虚线箭头还是实线箭头？以及需要activate合约吗？",
