    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我添加了Zoe在darksalmon的box里，合约调用Zoe之后deactivate合约，然后activate Zoe。接下来Zoe返回什么给合约？",
      "elements_involved": [
